quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  32,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  32,1,a l- meem
  32,2,iss kitaab ki Tanzil bulaa shuba rab alameen ki taraf se hai
  32,3,"kya yeh log kehte hain ke is shakhs ne isay khud ghurr liya hai? nahi, balkay yeh haq hai tairay rab ki taraf se taakay to mutnabba kere aik aisi qoum ko jis ke paas tujh se pehlay koi mutnabba karne wala nahi aaya, shayad ke woh hadaayat pa jayen"
  32,4,"woh Allah hi hai jis ne asmano aur zameen ko aur unn saari cheezon ko jo un ke darmain hain chay dinon mein peda kya aur is ke baad arsh par jalva farma howa, uss ke siwa nah tumhara koi haami o madad gaar hai aur nah koi uss ke agay sifarish karne wala, phir kya tum hosh mein nah aao ge ?"
  32,5,woh aasman se zameen taq duniya ke mamlaat ki tadbeer karta hai aur is tadbeer ki rudaad ooper uss ke huzoor jati hai aik aisay din mein jis ki miqdaar tumahray shumaar se aik hazaar saal hai
  32,6,"wohi hai har posheeda aur zahir ka jan-nay wala, zabardast, aur Raheem"
  32,7,jo cheez bhi is ne banai khoob hi banai aُ seen ne ensaan ki takhleeq ki ibtida gaaray se ki
  32,8,phir uss ki nasal aik aisay sat se chalaye jo haqeer pani ki terhan ka hai
  32,9,"phir is ko nick suck se durust kya aur is ke andar apni rooh phoonk di, aur tum ko kaan diye, ankhen den aur dil diye tum log kam hi shukar guzaar hotay ho"
  32,10,"aur yeh log kehte hain :"" jab hum matti mein rel mil chuke hon ge to kya hum phir naye suray se peda kiye jayen ge ?"" asal baat yeh hai ke yeh apne rab ki mulaqaat ke munkir hain"
  32,11,"inn se kaho"" mout ka woh farishta jo tum par muqarrar kya gaya hai tum ko poora ka poora apne qabzay mein le le ga aur phir tum apne rab ki taraf palta laaye jao ge """
  32,12,"kash tum dekho woh waqt jab yeh mujrim sir jukaye apne rab ke huzoor kharray hon ge ( uss waqt yeh keh rahay hon ge )"" ae hamaray rab, hum ne khoob dekh liya aur sun liya ab hamein wapas bhaij day taakay hum naik amal karen, hamein ab yaqeen agaya hai """
  32,13,"( jawab mein irshad ho ga )"" agar hum chahtay to pehlay hi har nafs ko is ki hadaayat day dete magar meri woh baat poori ho gayi jo mein ne kahi thi ke mein Jahannum ko junoo aur insanon sab se bhar dun ga"
  32,14,"pas ab chako maza apni iss harkat ka ke tum ne is din ki mulaqaat ko faramosh kar diya, hum ne bhi ab tumhe faramosh kar diya hai chako hameshgi ke azaab ka maza apne krtoton ki Padaash mein """
  32,15,hamari ayaat par to woh log imaan laatay hain jinhein yeh ayaat suna kar jab nasiyaat ki jati hai to sjday mein gir parte hain aur apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karte hain aur taqqabur nahi karte
  32,16,"unn ki پیٹھیں bistaron se allag rehti hain, apne rab ko khauf aur tama ke sath pukarte hain, aur jo kuch rizaq hum ne unhen diya hai is mein se kharch karte hain"
  32,17,phir jaissa kuch aankhon ki thandak ka samaan un ke aamaal ki jaza mein un ke liye chhupa rakha gaya hai is ki kisi mutnaqas ko khabar nahi hai
  32,18,bhala kahin yeh ho sakta hai ke jo shakhs momin ho woh uss shakhs ki terhan ho jaye jo fasik ho? yeh dono barabar nahi ho satke
  32,19,"jo log imaan laaye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain unn ke liye tojannaton ki qiyam gahay hain, ziyafat ke tor par unn ke aamaal ke badlay mein"
  32,20,aur jinhon ne fisq ikhtiyar kya hai unn ka thikana dozakh hai jab kabhi woh is se niklana chahain ge isi mein dhakel diye jayen ge aur un se kaha jaye ga ke chako ab usi aag ke azaab ka maza jis ko tum jhatlaya karte thay
  32,21,"uss barray azaab se pehlay hum isi duniya mein ( kisi nah kisi chhootey ) azaab ka maza aِnhin چکھاتے rahen ge, shayad ke yeh ( apni baghiana rawish se ) baz aa jayen"
  32,22,aur uss se bara zalim kon ho ga jisay is ke rab ki ayaat ke zareya se nasiyaat ki jaye aur phir woh un se mun phair le aisay mujrimon se to hum intiqam le kar rahen ge
  32,23,"iss se pehlay hum moose ko kitaab day chuke hain, lehaza usi cheez ke milnay par tumhe koi shak nah hona chahiye uss kitaab ko hum ne bani Israel ke liye hadaayat banaya tha"
  32,24,aur jab unhon ne sabr kya aur hamari ayaat par yaqeen laatay rahay to un ke andar hum ne aisay peshwa peda kiye jo hamaray hukum se rahnumai karte thay
  32,25,yaqeenan tera rab hi qayamat ke roz unn baton ka faisla kere ga jin mein ( bani Israel ) baahum ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain
  32,26,"aur kya inn logon ko ( inn tareekhi waqeat mein ) koi hadaayat nahi mili ke un se pehlay kitni qomon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain jin ke rehne ki jaghon mein aaj yeh chaltay phirtay hain? is mein barri nishanain hain, kya yeh suntay nahi hain ?"
  32,27,"aur kya inn logon ne yeh manzar kabhi nahi dekha ke hum aik be aabb o giyah zameen ki taraf pani baha laatay hain, aur phir isi zameen se woh fasal ogatay hain jis se un ke janwaron ko bhi charah milta hai aur yeh khud bhi khatay hain? to kya inhen kuch nahi sujhta ?"
  32,28,"yeh log kehte hain ke"" yeh faisla kab ho ga agar tum sachey ho? """
  32,29,"un se kaho"" faislay ke din imaan lana unn logon ke liye kuch bhi nafea nah ho ga jinhon ne kufar kya hai aur phir unn ko koi mohlat nah miley gi """
  32,30,"acha, aِnhin un ke haal par chore do aur intzaar karo, yeh bhi muntazir hain"
